		<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><strong><br />“赛龙夺锦”庆端午音乐会</strong><strong> </strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">时间：<span style="font-family: Calibri;">2013</span>年<span style="font-family: Calibri;">6</span>月<span style="font-family: Calibri;">8</span>日<span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>晚<span style="font-family: Calibri;">19:30</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">地点：民族音乐厅</span></p>
<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">
<p style="text-align: center;">主持人：高文进</p>
 
<p> </p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">一、打击乐组合《赛龙舟》<span style="font-family: Calibri;">                                                                </span>李文博编曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                    演奏：李文博等</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">二、笛子独奏《幽兰逢春》                                                         <span style="font-family: Calibri;">  赵松庭 曹星</span>曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                  演奏：马芸（文华奖获奖者）    <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>钢琴伴奏：刘迎旭</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">三、三弦独奏《边寨之夜》                                                                   <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>费坚蓉曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                      演奏：张馨元</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">四、丝弦五重奏《天山之春》<span style="font-family: Calibri;">                       </span>乌斯满江、俞礼纯曲<span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>王范地改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                             《欢乐的夜晚》                                                          <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>胡登跳曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                     演奏：马英俊等</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">五、广东音乐《平湖秋月》<span style="font-family: Calibri;">                                                                </span>刘明源改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                         《双声恨》                                                                 <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>刘明源改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                        高胡演奏：刘湘（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">六、古琴与箫《阳关三叠》                                                                          <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>古曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                       《梅花三弄》<span style="font-family: Calibri;">                                                                            </span>古曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                          古琴演奏：邓红<span style="font-family: Calibri;">        </span>萧：马芸</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">七、扬琴独奏《将军令》                                                                      <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>民间乐曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                          演奏：马英俊</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">八、钢琴与民乐《春江花月夜》<span style="font-family: Calibri;">                                                                   </span>古曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                             《青花瓷》                                                                 <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>周杰伦曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                         演奏：刘迎旭等</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">九、唢呐与钢琴打击乐《雪<span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>梅》<span style="font-family: Calibri;">                                                          </span>左继承曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                           演奏：陈力宝</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">十、琵琶独奏《龙船》                                                                          <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>民间乐曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                       演奏：蒋彦（<span style="font-family: Calibri;">CCTV</span>十大青年琵琶演奏家）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">十一、中胡独奏《草原上》                                                                  <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>刘明源曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                            演奏：刘湘</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">十二、合奏《节日的欢乐》                                                                  <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>刘明源曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                  新疆木碗唢呐演奏：陈力宝</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                        手鼓演奏：李文博</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: medium;">十三、合奏《新编喜洋洋——幸福年》                             <span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>刘明源曲<span style="font-family: Calibri;"> </span>刘湘改编</span></p>
